@alsal1985 Aramaic language was not the birth language of the Messiah of the Bible. 35 seconds into this video the guy in the video made this claim let’s go to the Scriptures. Acts chapter 26 verse 14. And when we were all fallen to the earth, I heard a voice speaking unto me, and saying in the Hebrew tongue, Saul, Saul, why persecutest thou me? it is hard for thee to kick against the pricks
Saul also spoke Hebrew. all of the 12 tribes of Israel spoke Hebrew.
All praises to YAH HIS Hebrew name

